criminal CODE 
Mr. Speaker , Canadians have always been frustrated that a life sentence in this country is in fact not a life sentence . 
for example , Clifford Olson murdered several children yet had a chance for a review at 15 years , called the faint hope clause . 
my bill would simply repeal section 745 of the criminal code including any relevant sections . 
